response.overview: DVD of the sold out Reverze party in Antwerp sportpalace held on the 22nd of February 2010. The Magic Box exploded and unleashed a fury of light, fire, laser and pounding beats over 16.000 visitors and two spectacular stages. Reverze, bigger, better and harder than ever before. If You want to experience the damage it did… here’s your chance. Enjoy!
response.title: Reverze 2010 Revelations The Live Registration
